\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Cozumel Reef Resilience (2015\'962024)\
\
**Coral Reef Health in Cozumel (2015\'962024): Sustained Resilience and the Impact of the 2024 Bleaching Event**\
\
## Project Overview\
\
This project analyzes the evolution of coral reef health in **Cozumel** between **2015 and 2024**, comparing local trends with the national average for Mexico and other reef subregions in Quintana Roo.\
\
The analysis integrates three independent environmental datasets:\
\
- **NOAA Coral Reef Watch** \'96 Sea surface thermal stress measured using Degree Heating Weeks (DHW).\
- **GBIF (Global Biodiversity Information Facility)** \'96 Georeferenced coral occurrence records obtained through the GBIF API.\
- **Healthy Reefs Initiative (HRI)** \'96 Reef Health Index values compiled from official Report Cards.\
\
The objective is to explore whether changes in reef health coincide with periods of elevated thermal stress and changes in coral community composition.\
\
> **Note:** This is an exploratory data analysis project. The observed relationships represent temporal associations and should not be interpreted as evidence of causation.\
